{"tid":2170361,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗撚發現根本走唔出元朗嘅魔爪","createTime":"2020-08-23T08:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T06:01:52.000Z","uid":243540,"like":15,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a5b5c7bdbb0936ce7ec45a7147d378feba8b8f","tid":2170361,"uid":243540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"利申元朗已經行到厭晒<br />\n有時星期六日想出去行下<br />\n但係發覺元朗幾乎乜都有<br />\n根本唔洗出去<br />\n千色UNY，一田呢啲大型超市已經唔洗講<br />\n講街市，有合益同大橋街市<br />\n平時叫雞有利群樓同一堆神秘房<br />\n戲院又有元朗戲院同yoho<br />\n買衫更加唔洗講，成個yoho同大馬路都係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想買書有三聯<br />\n想買模型玩具有榮興<br />\n網吧有藍天,天堂<br />\n想買傢私又有鍵榮,實惠<br />\n想做gym又有<br />\n想買文具有元朗,光明書局<br />\n想買game 電腦野有喜利<br />\n想補習有遵理<br />\n最後講野食，成個雞地都係食肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食糖水又有B仔,食沾面有彩,鋸扒有安娜,食咖哩有石岡咖哩屋<br />\n基本上要食乜都有<br />\n<br />\n所以如果唔係especially要去某一間餐廳/舖頭，我根本諗唔到理由要離開元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望元朗可以少人啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c788c534ddc09eaaf4ae4ecec209f93a5042584","tid":2170361,"uid":366691,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"仲有鄉黑添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cdda7597e073e3fc25dcf65adb361af0638f32","tid":2170361,"uid":1249,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"有撚人入去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大西北撚算9數啦"},{"pid":"7ad9a458dcba4b767f201d6c601612f05596b89e","tid":2170361,"uid":252840,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"三聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets